import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import {log} from "ng-zorro-antd/core/logger"; import {TestInterfaceService} from "../pages-service/test-interface.service"; enum PageType { All, AE_AI, AE_DEAL, WR_AI, WR_DEAL, OL_AI, OL_DEAL } @Component({ selector: 'app-ssl-dialog-manage', templateUrl: './ssl-dialog-manage.component.html', styleUrls: ['./ssl-dialog-manage.component.scss'] }) export class SslDialogManageComponent { currentPageType:PageType; tabs = [1, 2, 3]; constructor(private service:TestInterfaceService) { this.currentPageType = PageType.All this.getData(); } getData(){ this.service.getIdenty({}).subscribe((dic: any)=>{ console.log("getData====", dic); }) } changePage(index:PageType){ log("index", index); this.currentPageType = index; } }
